  },
  {
    "slug": "checklist-setup",
    "type": "text",
    "meta": {
      "section_group": "setup",
      "section_title": "Antes de começar"
    },
    "content": {
      "body": "## Antes de começar\n\n### Checklist de Setup\n- **Node.js 18+** instalado\n- **Claude Code CLI** instalado globalmente\n- **API Key** da Anthropic ou Claude Max ativo\n- **Git** configurado\n- **Projeto do exercício** clonado\n\n### Setup do projeto\n```bash\ngit clone https://github.com/coutoluizf/workshop-claude-code-exercises.git\ncd workshop-claude-code-exercises/modulo-01\nnpm install && npm test\n```"
    }
  },
  {
    "slug": "setup-testes-falham",
    "type": "callout",
    "meta": {
      "section_group": "setup",
